    public interface LireFeature
extends FeatureVector
    This is the basic interface for all content based features. Created by mlux on 28/05/2008.
    Author:
    Mathias Lux, mathias@juggle.at, Nektarios Anagnostopoulos, nek.anag@gmail.com
